data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home in Rockville MD the living room features a gorgeous fireplace and built in shelving. The kitchen has all the counter space you could ever want, and the spacious fenced in backyard with private pool. This home features 3 bedrooms with hardwood floors throughout and 2.5 baths, Master bedroom with private bath with two bedrooms and full bath upstairs. Down on the bottom level full washer and dryer with plenty of storage space. Call your agents to schedule a showing today!
